Minimalistic style: A pristine white envelope floating in a vast empty space, deconstructed into geometric segments that form a grid pattern resembling a spreadsheet or matrix. Each segment connects to others through thin, elegant lines suggesting pathways and relationships. The envelope casts soft shadows in muted blues and grays. Small abstract symbols—circles, squares, arrows—orbit around the envelope like satellites, representing different actions and operations. The composition is clean, airy, and mathematical, with generous negative space and a subtle gradient background shifting from pale cream to soft lavender.
